  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Giardino Verdi's family run atmosphere is obvious the moment you step through the door; the Moreschi family are very welcoming and will make you feel right at home.</p>
<h2>Great for couples and small groups</h2>
<p>The hotel's large outdoor terrace is a particular highlight and the perfect place to relax with friends and family whilst enjoying the delicious home-cooked regional dishes. It prides itself in being a contemporary getaway for couples and small groups of friends who want a really chilled out atmosphere to come back to at the end of the day.</p>]]></description>
