  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Media Twin Rooms</strong> are around 22m² and sleep up to two people. Rooms can also be made up as a double, please request at time of booking. </p>
<p><strong>Large Double Rooms</strong> are around 24m² and sleep up to two people. They have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Smart Double Rooms for sole use</strong> are also available.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Shower stall</li>
<li>Mini fridge</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>General Information</strong></p>
<p><strong>Check-in: </strong>2pm</p>
<p><strong>Check-out: </strong>10am</p>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A tourist tax of approx. €2.50 per person per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
